   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="letter" xml:id="d3e153">
            <pb n="1" facs="0012_000192_000203_0001.jpg" xml:id="d3e154"/>
            <p>Knoxville Tenn</p>
            <p>Nov. 16./63.</p>
            <pb n="2" facs="0012_000192_000203_0002.jpg" xml:id="d3e164"/>
            <p>Knoxville Tenn.</p>
            <p>Nov. 16th 8 o&apos;c <unclear reason="illegible" resp="JCM">PM</unclear>
            </p>
            <p>Dear Father</p>
            <p>We are here all right <unclear reason="illegible" resp="JCM">excepting</unclear> some small <unclear reason="illegible" resp="JCM">lopes -</unclear> the rebs. made us &quot;get back&quot;-</p>
            <p>I am all right - the nearest I came to being shot was a bullet in my coat collar.</p>
            <p>Dont worry about me. I am well &amp; in good spirits.</p>
            <p>With much love to all of you</p>
            <p>Your son</p>
            <p>Watson</p>
         </div>
      </body>
